 __(a) with dative (Polyb., al.; Refs [1Ma.1:43, I Est 4:39): 2Th 2:12]; 
 __(b) as freq. in LXX, 
 __α with accusative: Refs [Mat 12:13, Heb 10:5, 8 (LXX)] ; 
