G2398:
ἴδιος [G:A]
one's own/private — ἴδιος, -α, -ον (in Attic usually -ος, -ον), 
 [in LXX chiefly for of person(s) suff., also for לָהֶם, etc.; (τὰ ἴ.) בֵּיתוֹ ;] 
