 __(b) to execute, accomplish, carry out to the full: Refs [Mat 3:15, Luk 7:1 9:31, Act 12:25 13:25 14:26 19:21, Rom 8:4 13:8 15:19, Gal 5:14, Col 1:25 4:17, Rev 6:11], T, WH, R, mg.; 
