 __(b) as in cl., of homage to human superiors (cf. MM, xxi): absol., Refs [Mat 20:20, Act 10:25]; with dative (see supr.), Refs [Mat 2:2, 8 8:2 9:18 14:33 15:25 18:26 28:9, Mrk 15:19, Jhn 9:38]; πεσὼν., Refs [Mat 2:11 4:9]; ἐνώπιον τ. ποδῶν, Rev 3:9; with accusative, Mrk 5:6 (dative T).†

